Package dev.lazurite.thimble.example.composition

Class FloatAwayComposition

java.lang.Object
dev.lazurite.thimble.composition.Composition
dev.lazurite.thimble.example.composition.FloatAwayComposition
public class FloatAwayComposition
extends Composition
This Composition causes any associated Entity to float upwards forever.
Author:
Ethan Johnson
